<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent031680d65cbd495886413878d0939e7f">
</div>
<p>Almond Care’s tailor-made packages of nurse-led complex care in the home for adults and children don’t stop at meeting clients’ clinical needs.</p>
<p>The firm handpicks dedicated care teams to help each of its of its clients live life to the full by helping them to maximise their independence.</p>
<p>Almond Care is committed to meeting the needs of clients living with the most complex requirements, such as brain injury, spinal cord injury, long-term ventilation, cerebral palsy, or multiple sclerosis – by providing nurse-led care in their own homes.</p>
<p>When a new client instructs Almond Care, the firm’s clinical specialists assess their needs and the specific provision they require. On this basis, it then recruits a dedicated team of care professionals to meet the holistic needs of the client, placing considerable emphasis on their character and personality.</p>
<p>Almond Care believes that care is about much more than nursing. That is why the firm handpicks staff who are experienced in areas such as mobility issues, personal hygiene, housekeeping, socialising, support for hobbies and interests, companionship and emotional support.</p>
<p>For a free, no-obligation discussion about Almond Care’s UK complex care in the home for brain injury, spinal cord injury, long-term ventilation, cerebral palsy, multiple sclerosis, muscular dystrophy and other neurological conditions, please call 024 7610 2333.</p>
<p> </p></div>
</div>
